title: Tensorflow 1.10.1 incompatible with latest numpy version 1.15.1
body_html:
Installed TF with following command pip3 install tensorflow. The installation is successful but gave me this error.
tensorflow 1.10.1 has requirement numpy<=1.14.5,>=1.13.3, but you'll have numpy 1.15.1 which is incompatible.

Do I need to downgrade my numpy version?
